# having a nice [[taste]], [[tasty]], [[good]], [[delicious]]
#: {{usex|Die kos het '''lekker''' gesmaak.|t=The food tasted '''nice'''.|lang=af}}
# good, [[fun]], [[nice]] in a more generic sense
#: {{usex|'''Lekker''' tye.|t='''Fun''' times|lang=af}}
# {{context|lang=af|informal}} [[foxy]], [[sexy]]
#: {{usex|Kyk na daai '''lekker''' ding|t=Look at that '''foxy''' lady|lang=af}}

